page.title: 02A DAY IN MY LIFE:D.Steeds.
page.content: I woke up at 7:15 and had breakfast about an hour later.I looked at the sports page in the Times which is the newspaper we get and then we all piled into the car to go to school.It took us about ten minutes to get to school then my brother and father dropped us off. In school we do English,Maths,Welsh and games.We have dinner in school and at 3:30p.m. we go home. My father{ picks us up from school.I have a piano lesson at 4:30 and at about 5:10 I come home and watch some television.We had a supper of spaghetti bolognaise which was lovely.After supper my brother and I went to the top of our garden to play football and cricket.We came back to the house to watch Cover Up and C.A.T.S. Eyes.After that we went upstairs to bed.We had a five minute read and then went to sleep.
